column5: spent 5 days fishin with 3 other guys ,,,boated over 40 fish combined mainly eyes but lots of bass and pan fih too.if you counted all fish it is well over 90........stayed at kirk cove.nice cabins and docks.the owners JIM -N-CLAIRE are good people and was there for our needs.this makes 9 yrs for me and ill be back..if you want the who what where pm me and i tell you what i know....and so long 4 now;john
